ORS 409.300 is amended to read:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none;tab-stops:30.0pt 60.0pt 90.0pt 120.0pt 150.0pt 180.0pt 210.0pt 240.0pt 270.0pt 300.0pt 330.0pt 360.0pt 390.0pt 420.0pt 450.0pt 480.0pt 510.0pt 540.0pt 570.0pt 600.0pt;
mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'><span style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>409.300. (1) There is
established the Domestic Violence Fund in the Services to Children and Families
Account of the General Fund established under ORS 409.260.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none;tab-stops:30.0pt 60.0pt 90.0pt 120.0pt 150.0pt 180.0pt 210.0pt 240.0pt 270.0pt 300.0pt 330.0pt 360.0pt 390.0pt 420.0pt 450.0pt 480.0pt 510.0pt 540.0pt 570.0pt 600.0pt;
mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'><span style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>(2) All moneys received
by the Director of Human Services under ORS 106.045 [<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:
normal'>(2)</i>] <b>or section 7 of this 2007 Act </b>and any other funds
allocated for expenditure under ORS 409.292 shall be credited to the Domestic
Violence Fund.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none;tab-stops:30.0pt 60.0pt 90.0pt 120.0pt 150.0pt 180.0pt 210.0pt 240.0pt 270.0pt 300.0pt 330.0pt 360.0pt 390.0pt 420.0pt 450.0pt 480.0pt 510.0pt 540.0pt 570.0pt 600.0pt;
mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt'><span style='mso-tab-count:1'>          </span>(3) All moneys credited
to the Domestic Violence Fund are continuously appropriated for the purposes of
ORS 409.292 to be expended by the director as provided in ORS 409.290 and
409.292. However, the director shall expend not more than 10 percent of such
moneys for administrative costs of the Department of Human Services incurred
under ORS 409.290 and 409.292.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-pagination:none;tab-stops:30.0pt 60.0pt 90.0pt 120.0pt 150.0pt 180.0pt 210.0pt 240.0pt 270.0pt 300.0pt 330.0pt 360.0pt 390.0pt 420.0pt 450.0pt 480.0pt 510.0pt 540.0pt 570.0pt 600.0pt;
